#: cps/templates/config_db.html:118
msgid ""
"If your Calibre library is corrupted and cannot be opened, you can attempt to restore it from the OPF files in your library. This will <b>erase all per-book data</b> (reading progress, bookmarks, shelf links, downloads, etc.) in the app database, but will not "
"affect user accounts or settings. <b>Both databases will be automatically backed up in /config/backup before any destructive action.</b> A restore log will be saved alongside the backups."
msgstr ""
"如果您的 Calibre 書庫損壞且無法開啟，您可以嘗試從書庫中的 OPF 檔案進行還原。這將<b>擦除應用程式資料庫中所有的每本書籍資料</b>（閱讀進度、\n"
"書籤、書架連結、下載次數等），但不會影響使用者帳號或設定。<b>在執行任何破壞性操作之前，兩個資料庫都會自動備份到 /config/backup 中。</b>還原日誌將與備份一起儲存。"

#: cps/templates/config_db.html:121
msgid "Are you sure? This cannot be undone."
msgstr "您確定嗎？此操作無法撤銷。"

