#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:136
msgid "Enable/Disable Calibre-Web Automated Services"
msgstr "啟用/停用 Calibre-Web Automated 服務"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:143
msgid "Enable CWA Auto-Convert"
msgstr "啟用 CWA 自動轉換"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:145
msgid ""
"On by default, when active all ingested books will automatically be converted to the target format specified below (epub by default) \n"
"        <em>EXCEPT</em> those you have specifically told CWA to ignore below."
msgstr "預設啟用。啟用時，所有匯入的書籍將自動轉換為下方指定的目標格式 (預設為 epub)，但下方特別設定忽略的書籍除外。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:154
msgid "Enable CWA Automatic Cover & Metadata Enforcement Service"
msgstr "啟用 CWA 自動封面與元數據強制執行服務"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:156
msgid ""
"On by default, when active, whenever the Metadata and/or Cover Image is edited in the Web UI, the CWA Metadata Enforcement service \n"
"        will then apply those changes the ebook files themselves. Normally in Stock CW or when this setting is disabled, the changes made \n"
"        are only applied to what you see in the Web UI, not the ebook files themselves. This feature currently only supports files in EPUB \n"
"        or AZW3 format."
msgstr "預設啟用。啟用後，每當在 Web UI 中編輯元數據或封面圖片時，CWA 元數據強制執行服務會將這些變更套用至電子書檔案本身。一般在原版 CW 或停用此設定時，變更僅套用至 UI 顯示，而非檔案本身。此功能目前僅支援 EPUB 或 AZW3 格式。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:167
msgid "Enable CWA Kindle EPUB Fixer"
msgstr "啟用 CWA Kindle EPUB 修復器"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:169
msgid ""
"When active, the encoding among other attributes of all EPUB files processed by CWA will be checked and fixed to ensure maximum \n"
"        compatibility with Amazon's Send-to-Kindle Service. This feature is particularly useful for users who frequently send EPUB files to their Kindle devices and have experienced issues with \n"
"        file rejections or formatting problems."
msgstr "啟用後，CWA 會檢查並修復所有處理中的 EPUB 檔案編碼及其它屬性，以確保與 Amazon Send-to-Kindle 服務的最大相容性。這對於經常發送 EPUB 到 Kindle 且曾遇過檔案被拒或格式問題的使用者特別有用。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:174
msgid "This tool was adapted from the <a href=\"https://kindle-epub-fix.netlify.app/\">kindle-epub-fix.netlify.app</a> tool made by <a href=\"https://github.com/innocenat\">innocenat</a>."
msgstr "此工具改編自 <a href=\"[https://github.com/innocenat](https://github.com/innocenat)\">innocenat</a> 製作的 <a href=\"[https://kindle-epub-fix.netlify.app/](https://kindle-epub-fix.netlify.app/)\">kindle-epub-fix.netlify.app</a>。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:181
msgid "Enable KOReader Sync (CWA Plugin)"
msgstr "啟用 KOReader 同步 (CWA 插件)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:183
msgid "When enabled, CWA exposes the /kosync endpoints and stores KOReader-compatible checksums in metadata.db for progress syncing. Requires the KOReader plugin on your device."
msgstr "啟用後，CWA 將開放 /kosync 端點並在 metadata.db 中儲存 KOReader 相容的校驗值以同步進度。您的裝置需安裝 KOReader 插件。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:185
msgid "Note: Enabling this starts a checksum backfill service at startup which can temporarily lock metadata.db. To stop a running backfill, restart the container after disabling."
msgstr "注意：啟用此功能會在啟動時開始校驗值回填服務，可能會暫時鎖定 metadata.db。若要停止執行中的回填，請在停用後重啟容器。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:192
msgid "Enable Aggressive EPUB Fixer Mode (riskier)"
msgstr "啟用激進 EPUB 修復模式 (較具風險)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:194
msgid "Aggressive mode applies more invasive fixes and will attempt lower-confidence encoding conversions. Safe mode is recommended for most libraries."
msgstr ""
"激進模式會套用更具侵入性的修復，並嘗試信賴度較低的編碼轉換。對於大多數書庫，\n"
"建議使用安全模式。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:202
msgid "Enable Archived Book Cleanup"
msgstr "啟用歸檔書籍清理"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:204
msgid "Removes stale archived book references in app.db when the book no longer exists in the Calibre library. Helps keep archived counts accurate."
msgstr "當書籍已不存在於 Calibre 書庫時，移除 app.db 中失效的歸檔書籍引用。有助於保持歸檔數量準確。"

