#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:302
msgid "Enable Automatic Metadata Fetching for New Books"
msgstr "啟用新書自動抓取元數據"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:304
msgid ""
"When active, CWA will automatically attempt to fetch and apply metadata (title, author, description, cover, etc.) for newly ingested books using the configured metadata provider hierarchy. This helps improve the quality of book information, especially for "
"books with poor or missing metadata."
msgstr "啟用後，CWA 會根據配置的供應商優先順序，自動為新匯入的書籍抓取並套用元數據 (書名、作者、描述、封面等)。這有助於提升書籍資訊品質，特別是針對資訊缺失的書籍。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:312
msgid "Enable Smart Metadata Application"
msgstr "啟用智慧元數據套用"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:314
msgid "When enabled, fetched metadata will only replace existing data if it appears to be better quality (e.g., longer descriptions, higher resolution covers). When disabled, fetched metadata will replace existing data as-is from the preferred provider."
msgstr "啟用後，僅當抓取到的元數據品質較佳 (例如描述更長、封面解析度更高) 時才會取代現有資料。停用時，則直接以首選供應商的資料覆蓋現有資料。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:319
msgid "Metadata Fields to Update"
msgstr "要更新的元數據欄位"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:321
msgid "Select which metadata fields should be updated when auto-fetching. Unchecked fields will never be modified during automatic metadata fetching, preserving your existing data."
msgstr "選擇自動抓取時應更新的欄位。未勾選的欄位在自動抓取過程中將永遠不會被修改，以保護您的現有資料。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:355 cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:357
msgid "Tags/Genres"
msgstr "標籤/類型"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:376 cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:378
msgid "Publication Date"
msgstr "出版日期"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:383 cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:385
msgid "Identifiers (ISBN, etc.)"
msgstr "識別碼 (ISBN 等)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:390 cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:392
msgid "Cover Image"
msgstr "封面圖片"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:398 cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:419 cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:526 cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:731 cps/templates/user_edit.html:389 cps/templates/user_edit.html:480
msgid "Tip"
msgstr "提示"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:398
msgid "These field selections apply to both Smart and Direct replacement modes. Smart mode will additionally apply quality criteria to selected fields, while Direct mode will replace all selected fields with provider data."
msgstr "這些欄位選擇同時適用於「智慧」和「直接」取代模式。智慧模式會對選定欄位額外套用品質判斷準則，而直接模式則會用供應商資料取代所有選定欄位。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:403
msgid "Cover File Max Size (MB):"
msgstr "封面檔案大小上限 (MB)："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:416
msgid "Range: 1-200 MB (default: 15)"
msgstr "範圍：1-200 MB (預設：15)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:419
msgid "Limits the maximum size of cover images downloaded from metadata providers or URLs to prevent slow or stalled saves."
msgstr "限制從供應商或網址下載的封面圖片大小上限，以防止儲存緩慢或停滯。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:428
msgid "Ingest Processing Timeout"
msgstr "匯入處理逾時"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:430
msgid "Maximum time (in minutes) to allow for processing a single book before timing out. Files that timeout are moved to the failed backup folder for investigation."
msgstr "處理單一書籍所允許的最長時間 (分鐘)。逾時的檔案將被移至失敗備份資料夾以供檢查。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:432
msgid "Timeout (minutes):"
msgstr "逾時時間 (分鐘)："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:444
msgid "Range: 5-120 minutes (default: 15)"
msgstr "範圍：5-120 分鐘 (預設：15)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:448
msgid "Stale temp cleanup"
msgstr "失效暫存清理"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:449
msgid "Ignored temporary upload files (.uploading, .part, etc.) can be cleaned after a set age. Setting either value to 0 disables cleanup. Changes apply on the next cleanup cycle."
msgstr "被忽略的暫存上傳檔案 (.uploading, .part 等) 可在達到設定時長後清理。任一數值設為 0 則停用清理。變更將於下次清理週期生效。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:454
msgid "Stale temp age (minutes):"
msgstr "暫存檔案保留時長 (分鐘)："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:467
msgid "Range: 0-10080 minutes (default: 120)"
msgstr "範圍：0-10080 分鐘 (預設：120)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:471
msgid "Stale temp cleanup interval (seconds):"
msgstr "暫存清理執行間隔 (秒)："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:484
msgid "Range: 0-86400 seconds (default: 600)"
msgstr "範圍：0-86400 秒 (預設：600)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:490
msgid "Auto-Send Delay for New Books"
msgstr "新書自動發送延遲"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:492
msgid "Delay (in minutes) before automatically sending newly ingested books to eReaders. This allows time for metadata fetching and other processing to complete before sending. Only applies to users who have enabled auto-send in their profile."
msgstr "新匯入書籍自動發送到閱讀器前的延遲時間 (分鐘)。這能在發送前留出時間完成元數據抓取及其它處理。僅適用於在個人資料中啟用了自動發送的使用者。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:494
msgid "Delay (minutes):"
msgstr "延遲 (分鐘)："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:506
msgid "Range: 1-60 minutes (default: 5)"
msgstr "範圍：1-60 分鐘 (預設：5)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:511
msgid "Auto Metadata Fetch Provider Hierarchy"
msgstr "自動元數據抓取供應商優先順序"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:513
msgid "Configure the order in which metadata providers are searched when automatically fetching metadata for new books. Drag and drop to reorder providers. Only enabled providers will be used."
msgstr "配置自動抓取新書元數據時的供應商搜尋順序。拖放可重新排序。僅會使用已啟用的供應商。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:526
msgid "Providers are tried in order from top to bottom. Drag to reorder."
msgstr "供應商將由上而下依序嘗試。請拖動來調整順序。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:535
msgid "Enabled Metadata Providers"
msgstr "已啟用的元數據供應商"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:537
msgid "Unchecked providers are disabled globally."
msgstr "未勾選的供應商將在全域範圍內停用。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:550
msgid "Hardcover Auto-Fetch Settings"
msgstr "Hardcover 自動抓取設定"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:552
msgid "Automatically fetch and assign Hardcover IDs to books in your library. Hardcover IDs enable reading progress sync and annotation sync with Hardcover.app when using compatible eReaders."
msgstr "自動抓取並為書庫中的書籍分配 Hardcover ID。Hardcover ID 能在使用相容的閱讀器時，與 Hardcover.app 同步閱讀進度和註解。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:557
msgid "Hardcover Token Required"
msgstr "需要 Hardcover Token"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:558
msgid "To enable Hardcover auto-fetch, you must set a valid HARDCOVER_TOKEN in your docker-compose environment variables or configure a global token in Basic Configuration. Without a valid token, this feature will remain disabled."
msgstr "要啟用 Hardcover 自動抓取，您必須在 docker-compose 環境變數中設定有效的 HARDCOVER_TOKEN，或在基本配置中設定全域 Token。若無有效 Token，此功能將維持停用。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:569
msgid "Enable Hardcover Auto-Fetch"
msgstr "啟用 Hardcover 自動抓取"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:571
msgid "Automatically search Hardcover for books without Hardcover IDs. High-confidence matches are applied automatically; low-confidence matches are queued for manual review."
msgstr "自動為沒有 Hardcover ID 的書籍搜尋 Hardcover 資料。高信賴度的匹配會自動套用；低信賴度的匹配則會進入隊列等待手動審核。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:576
msgid "Run Schedule:"
msgstr "執行排程："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:597
msgid "How often to automatically run the Hardcover ID fetch task"
msgstr "自動執行 Hardcover ID 抓取任務的頻率"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:677
msgid "Minimum Confidence Threshold:"
msgstr "最低信賴度門檻："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:687
msgid "Range: 0.50-1.00 (default: 0.85)"
msgstr "範圍：0.50-1.00 (預設：0.85)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:689
msgid "Matches with confidence scores above this threshold are automatically applied. Lower scores are queued for manual review. Higher values = fewer auto-matches but higher accuracy."
msgstr "高於此門檻的匹配將自動套用。較低的分數則需手動審核。數值越高，自動匹配越少但準確率越高。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:695
msgid "Batch Size:"
msgstr "單次處理數量 (Batch Size)："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:705
msgid "Range: 10-200 books per run (default: 50)"
msgstr "範圍：每次執行 10-200 本 (預設：50)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:707
msgid "Number of books to process in each scheduled run. Smaller batches reduce API load; larger batches process your library faster."
msgstr "每次排程執行處理的書籍數量。較小的數量可減輕 API 負擔；較大的數量則處理較快。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:713
msgid "Rate Limit Delay (seconds):"
msgstr "速率限制延遲 (秒)："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:723
msgid "Range: 0-60 seconds (default: 5.0)"
msgstr "範圍：0-60 秒 (預設：5.0)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:725
msgid "Delay between API requests to Hardcover. Prevents rate limiting and protects your API key. Uses exponential backoff on errors."
msgstr "存取 Hardcover API 的間隔時間。防止觸發速率限制並保護您的 API 金鑰。出錯時會使用指數退避機制。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:731
msgid "You can manually trigger the Hardcover auto-fetch task from the Admin panel at any time. Check the CWA Stats page to see progress and review queued matches that need manual approval."
msgstr "您可以隨時從管理面板手動觸發 Hardcover 自動抓取任務。請查看 CWA 統計頁面以了解進度，並審核需要手動批准的匹配項。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:738
msgid "Web UI Settings"
msgstr "網頁介面設定"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:745
msgid "Enable CWA Update Notifications"
msgstr "啟用 CWA 更新通知"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:747
msgid "When active, you will receive notifications in the Web UI when a new version of CWA is released"
msgstr "啟用後，當 CWA 發佈新版本時，您將在網頁介面收到通知"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:755
msgid "Enable Contribute Translations Notifications"
msgstr "啟用翻譯貢獻通知"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:757
msgid "When disabled, you will no longer receive notifications in the Web UI when using a language other than English if the translations for your chosen language are not complete."
msgstr "停用後，如果您使用的語言翻譯尚未完整，網頁介面將不再顯示提醒您參與翻譯的通知。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:765
msgid "Sync Magic Shelves to Kobo"
msgstr "同步魔法書架至 Kobo"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:767
msgid "When active, your Magic Shelves will be synced to your Kobo device as collections. Note: You must also enable Kobo Sync in Basic Configuration."
msgstr "啟用後，您的魔法書架將作為收藏集同步到您的 Kobo 裝置。注意：您還必須在基本配置中啟用 Kobo 同步。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:775
msgid "Enable Blurred Backgrounds on Mobile (&lt;768px)"
msgstr "在行動裝置上啟用模糊背景 (&lt;768px)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:777
msgid "When active, the blurred cover background effect is also rendered on small screens. Disable if you notice scrolling or animation lag."
msgstr "啟用後，模糊的封面背景效果也會在小螢幕上渲染。如果您感覺到捲動或動畫延遲，請將其停用。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:782
msgid "Automatic Backup Settings"
msgstr "自動備份設定"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:789
msgid "Enable CWA Import Auto-Backup"
msgstr "啟用 CWA 匯入自動備份"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:791
msgid "When active, a copy of all imported files will be stored in <i>/config/processed_books/imported</i>"
msgstr "啟用後，所有匯入檔案的副本將儲存在 <i>/config/processed_books/imported</i> 中"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:799
msgid "Enable CWA Conversion Auto-Backup"
msgstr "啟用 CWA 轉換自動備份"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:801
msgid "When active, the originals of ingested files that undergo conversion will be stored in /config/processed_books/converted"
msgstr "啟用後，進行轉換的匯入檔案原檔將儲存在 /config/processed_books/converted 中"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:809
msgid "Enable CWA EPUB Fixer Auto-Backup"
msgstr "啟用 CWA EPUB 修復器自動備份"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:811
msgid "When active, the originals of EPUBs processed by the CWA Kindle EPUB Fixer service will be stored in /config/processed_books/fixed_originals"
msgstr "啟用後，由 CWA Kindle EPUB 修復服務處理的 EPUB 原檔將儲存在 /config/processed_books/fixed_originals 中"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:821
msgid "Enable CWA Auto-Zip Backups"
msgstr "啟用 CWA 自動壓縮備份"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:823
msgid ""
"When active, just before midnight each day, the cwa-auto-zipper service will make zip archives of all the backed up converted, imported and failed files from that day. This is to help keep the subdirectories of /config/processed_books organised and to minimise "
"disk space usage."
msgstr "啟用後，cwa-auto-zipper 服務每天午夜前會將當天備份的轉換、匯入及失敗檔案製作成 ZIP 封存檔。這有助於保持 /config/processed_books 子目錄的整潔並減少磁碟空間占用。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:828
msgid "CWA Auto-Conversion Target Format - EPUB by Default"
msgstr "CWA 自動轉換目標格式 - 預設為 EPUB"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:831
msgid "When the Auto-Convert feature is active, all ingested books will be automatically converted to the format chosen here (except those formats selected in the ignore list below)"
msgstr "啟用自動轉換功能時，所有匯入的書籍將自動轉換為此處選擇的格式 (下方忽略清單中選取的格式除外)。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:833
msgid "Choose a target format:"
msgstr "選擇目標格式："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:845
msgid "Note: CWA's Metadata Enforcement service can currently only support file in either EPUB and AZW3 format. Files in other formats will simply be ignored by the service"
msgstr "注意：CWA 的元數據強制執行服務目前僅支援 EPUB 和 AZW3 格式。其他格式的檔案將被該服務忽略"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:851
msgid "CWA Auto-Convert - Ignored Formats"
msgstr "CWA 自動轉換 - 忽略格式"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:853
msgid "The formats selected here will be ignored by CWA's Auto-Conversion feature when it's active, meaning they will be imported as is."
msgstr "啟用時，此處選取的格式將被 CWA 的自動轉換功能忽略，這意味著它們將按原樣匯入。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:878
msgid "CWA Auto-Convert - Retained Formats"
msgstr "CWA 自動轉換 - 保留格式"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:880
msgid ""
"The formats selected here will always be added to the library, even after they have been converted to the target format. However, if the format is in the \"CWA Auto-Ingest - Ignored Formats\" list, it will not be imported. Note that the target format is always "
"retained."
msgstr "此處選取的格式即使在轉換為目標格式後，也始終會被添加到書庫中。但是，如果該格式位於「CWA 自動匯入 - 忽略格式」清單中，則不會被匯入。請注意，目標格式始終會保留。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:907
msgid "CWA Auto-Ingest Automerge"
msgstr "CWA 自動匯入自動合併"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:910
msgid "Calibre can detect Duplicate Book Titles on Import and depending on the"
msgstr "Calibre 可以在匯入時偵測重複的書名，並根據"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:910
msgid "automerge"
msgstr "自動合併"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:911
msgid "setting. It can be set to delete either instance of a duplicated book or keep both (default)."
msgstr "設定，可以設定為刪除重複書籍的任一執行個體或兩者都保留 (預設)。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:929
msgid "Discards duplicate import, keeps library copy"
msgstr "捨棄重複的匯入，保留書庫中的副本"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:933
msgid "Overwrites library copy with newly imported file"
msgstr "使用新匯入的檔案覆寫書庫中的副本"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:937
msgid "Creates a duplicate record, keeping both copies"
msgstr "建立重複記錄，保留兩個副本"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:943
msgid "CWA Auto-Ingest - Ignored Formats"
msgstr "CWA 自動匯入 - 忽略格式"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:945
msgid "The formats selected here will be ignored by CWA's Auto-Ingest feature, meaning files in these formats won't be added to the library by CWA during the ingest process"
msgstr "此處選取的格式將被 CWA 的自動匯入功能忽略，這意味著 CWA 在匯入過程中不會將這些格式的檔案添加到書庫中"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:970
msgid "CWA Duplicate Detection System"
msgstr "CWA 重複項偵測系統"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:973
msgid "Enable or disable the duplicate detection system. When disabled, duplicate scanning will not run and no notifications will be shown."
msgstr "啟用或停用重複項偵測系統。停用時，重複項掃描將不會執行，且不會顯示任何通知。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:978
msgid "Enable Duplicate Detection"
msgstr "啟用重複項偵測"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:982
msgid "When enabled, CWA will scan for duplicate books after each import"
msgstr "啟用後，CWA 將在每次匯入後掃描重複的書籍"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:990
msgid "Duplicate Detection Method"
msgstr "重複項偵測方法"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:993
msgid "Hybrid (SQL prefilter + Python validation)"
msgstr "混合 (SQL 預過濾 + Python 驗證)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:996
msgid "Python only (slowest, most robust)"
msgstr "僅 Python (最慢但最健全)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:999
msgid "Legacy SQL only (experimental)"
msgstr "僅舊版 SQL (實驗性)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1005
msgid "Hybrid mode uses a fast SQL pre-filter to narrow candidates, then applies the robust Python logic for final results."
msgstr "混合模式使用快速的 SQL 預過濾器來縮小候選範圍，然後應用健全的 Python 邏輯來獲得最終結果。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1014
msgid "Automatic Duplicate Scanning"
msgstr "自動重複項掃描"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1017
msgid "Configure background duplicate scans. These run automatically without blocking the UI."
msgstr "配置背景重複項掃描。這些掃描會自動執行且不會阻塞使用者介面。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1022
msgid "Enable automatic duplicate scans"
msgstr "啟用自動重複項掃描"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1026
msgid "After import scans"
msgstr "匯入後掃描"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1029
msgid "Run after each import (debounced)"
msgstr "每次匯入後執行 (防抖動)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1032
msgid "Manual only"
msgstr "僅手動"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1038
msgid "After import debounce (seconds)"
msgstr "匯入後防抖動 (秒)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1046
msgid "Wait this many seconds after the last import before starting a background scan."
msgstr "在最後一次匯入後等待此秒數，然後才開始背景掃描。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1051
msgid "Scheduled scans (cron expression)"
msgstr "排程掃描 (cron 表達式)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1057
msgid "Leave blank to disable scheduled scans. Example:"
msgstr "留空以停用排程掃描。範例："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1062
msgid "If enabled, after-import scans and cron scans can both run. Use “Manual only” to disable after-import scans while keeping cron schedules."
msgstr "如果啟用，匯入後掃描和 cron 掃描都可以執行。使用「僅手動」可在保留 cron 排程的同時停用匯入後掃描。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1069 cps/templates/duplicates.html:398
msgid "Next scheduled scan:"
msgstr "下次預定掃描："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1076
msgid "CWA Duplicate Detection Criteria"
msgstr "CWA 重複項偵測標準"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1079
msgid "Configure which metadata fields are used to determine if books are duplicates. Books must match ALL selected criteria to be considered duplicates."
msgstr "配置使用哪些元數據欄位來判斷書籍是否重複。書籍必須符合所有選定的標準才會被視為重複。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1086
msgid "Consider book titles when detecting duplicates"
msgstr "偵測重複項時考慮書名"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1092
msgid "Consider book authors when detecting duplicates"
msgstr "偵測重複項時考慮作者"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1098
msgid "Consider book language when detecting duplicates"
msgstr "偵測重複項時考慮語言"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1104
msgid "Consider book series when detecting duplicates"
msgstr "偵測重複項時考慮叢書"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1110
msgid "Consider book publisher when detecting duplicates"
msgstr "偵測重複項時考慮出版社"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1115
msgid "Format"
msgstr "格式"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1116
msgid "Consider file format when detecting duplicates"
msgstr "偵測重複項時考慮檔案格式"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1122 cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1208
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "注意："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1122
msgid "At least one criterion must be selected. Title and Author are recommended as core criteria."
msgstr "必須至少選擇一個標準。建議將書名和作者作為核心標準。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1128
msgid "Duplicate Format Priority Ranking"
msgstr "重複項格式優先順序排名"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1131
msgid "Configure which file formats are preferred when using the \"Highest Quality Format\" auto-resolution strategy. Drag and drop to reorder formats by priority (higher = better)."
msgstr "配置在使用「最高品質格式」自動解決策略時偏好哪些檔案格式。透過拖放按優先級重新排序格式 (越高越好)。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1144
msgid "Tip:"
msgstr "提示："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1144
msgid "When resolving duplicates with \"Highest Quality Format\" strategy, books with higher-ranked formats will be kept. Lower priority formats will be deleted."
msgstr "當使用「最高品質格式」策略解決重複項時，將保留具有較高排名格式的書籍。低優先級格式將被刪除。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1152
msgid "Duplicate Notifications & Auto-Resolution"
msgstr "重複項通知與自動解決"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1155
msgid "Configure how you are notified about duplicate books and optionally enable automatic resolution."
msgstr "配置您如何收到關於重複書籍的通知，並選擇性地啟用自動解決。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1160
msgid "Enable Duplicate Notifications"
msgstr "啟用重複項通知"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1162
msgid "Show popup notifications when unresolved duplicates are detected. Admins and users with edit rights will see a badge on the Duplicates sidebar button and a notification popup when they login."
msgstr "偵測到未解決的重複項時顯示彈出通知。管理員和具有編輯權限的使用者將在側邊欄的「重複項」按鈕上看到標記，並在登入時看到通知彈窗。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1166
msgid "Enable Automatic Duplicate Resolution"
msgstr "啟用重複項自動解決"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1169 cps/templates/duplicates.html:437
msgid "Warning:"
msgstr "警告："

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1169
msgid "This will automatically delete books based on the strategy below. Original files will be backed up to"
msgstr "這將根據下方的策略自動刪除書籍。原始檔案將備份至"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1173
msgid "Auto-Resolution Strategy"
msgstr "自動解決策略"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1176
msgid "Keep Newest"
msgstr "保留最新"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1176
msgid "Delete older copies, keep the most recently added book"
msgstr "刪除較舊的副本，保留最近添加的書籍"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1179
msgid "Keep Oldest"
msgstr "保留最舊"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1179
msgid "Delete newer copies, keep the earliest added"
msgstr "刪除較新的副本，保留最早添加的書籍"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1182
msgid "Merge Formats"
msgstr "合併格式"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1182
msgid "Merge formats into the newest book, delete the rest"
msgstr "將格式合併到最新的書籍中，刪除其餘書籍"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1185
msgid "Keep Highest Quality Format"
msgstr "保留最高品質格式"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1185
msgid "Prefer formats based on your Duplicate Format Priority Ranking"
msgstr "根據您的重複項格式優先順序排名來偏好格式"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1188
msgid "Keep Most Metadata"
msgstr "保留最多元數據"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1188
msgid "Keep book with most complete information"
msgstr "保留資訊最完整的書籍"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1191
msgid "Keep Largest File Size"
msgstr "保留最大檔案大小"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1191
msgid "Keep book with largest total file size"
msgstr "保留總檔案大小最大的書籍"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1194
msgid "Choose which book to keep when duplicates are automatically resolved."
msgstr "選擇自動解決重複項時要保留哪本書。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1198
msgid "Rate Limiting"
msgstr "頻率限制"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1199
msgid "Cooldown Period (minutes)"
msgstr "冷卻時間 (分鐘)"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1203
msgid "Minimum time between automatic resolutions (0 to disable). Prevents rapid-fire deletions during batch imports."
msgstr "自動解決之間的最短時間 (0 表示停用)。防止在批次匯入期間發生連續刪除。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_settings.html:1208
msgid "Auto-resolution runs after duplicate scans detect new duplicates. Dismissed duplicate groups are never auto-resolved."
msgstr "自動解決會在重複項掃描偵測到新重複項後執行。已忽略的重複分組絕不會被自動解決。"

#: cps/templates/cwa_stats.html:66 cps/templates/cwa_stats_system.html:58
